creator: Medinet Australia Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
The Medinet Patient App allows you to:

- Consult with an actual doctor for scripts and medical certificates
- Book an appointment with medical centres on our platform
- Self check-in of your appointment using your personal QR code with medical centres on our platform
- Be notified of medical results when it is received by the medical practice
- Use your profile to book into Myhealth Medical Centres without completing a New Patient form.
 
all from the convenience of your mobile device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Medication delivery available Australia wide
Revised UX of saving personal information
Removed 'day' from Medicare expiry date input
Updated T&Cs and Privacy Policy
Enable ability to register on behalf of a child
Updated advice on pathology collection centres
And more!
